parameters: \bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Phew, I'm tired. Is that it for today?

\bustMoveTo[2, -100, 720, 30]\nc<Senpai>Yes, you did well. It seems the client is satisfied too.
Just be careful, if by any chance we get a bad review, we
might have to go through even more trouble.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Oh, is that so? (Well, a genius succubus like me wouldn't
have to worry about that!)

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Of course not. Normally after a blowjob kiss, you'd wash
your mouth once and then immediately move on to the next
client.

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>But this time I'll make an exception. Once you go back to
the office and write the business report, you can leave.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>A report... Do I have to write one every single time?

\nc<Senpai>Of course. The higher-ups love to see us suffer through
pointless paperwork.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>When you put it that way, I don't even know how to
respond...
\nc<Senpai>Saki, you just need to do as I say.

\nc<>Afterwards, she suffered through the pointless paperwork and
left work late at night.
